snippet.title: Ninja Game
snippet.description: Ninja Game Action game. Bounce, jump, fight, throw or run and become the best of all ninja's ever lived.

snippet.title: Gunshot Cowboy
snippet.description: Gunshot Cowboy Shooting game. Each level you must ride your horse and use guns to destroy the enemy units.

snippet.title: Bearboy and the Cursor
snippet.description: Bearboy and the Cursor Help the Bear in this platform game using the cursor to activate the level elements.

snippet.title: Lost Kingdom Prophecy
snippet.description: Lost Kingdom Prophecy Puzzle game. Find the missing elements and play match-3 or more games to complete the quest.

snippet.title: Stonehenge Solitaire
snippet.description: Stonehenge Solitaire Card game. Various types of the cards game solitaire can be played. Prove your cardplayer skills!

snippet.title: Water Buboy
snippet.description: Water Buboy Extinguish all of the fires and save the people using a limited amount of water.

snippet.title: Cowboy Bullet
snippet.description: Cowboy Bullet You are a Cowboy Bullet. As a bullet, you must try to hit as many coins as you can.

snippet.title: Colacoa BMX
snippet.description: Colacoa BMX Perform sick tricks on your BMX and get to the finish line within 5 minutes to go to the next level.

snippet.title: BMX Pro Style
snippet.description: BMX Pro Style Score as many points as possible by performing crazy tricks with your BMX.

snippet.title: Troglodytes 2
snippet.description: Troglodytes 2 Boardgame. Multiply your units and make sure to reach the other side and crush your opponent.
